data.description: This move-in ready, 1 1/2story home features 4 bedrooms in Spring Terrace and is sure to check all the boxes. Some features in an open concept first floor flowing from kitchen to family room. All appliances including refrigerator and washer/dryer are included with the home. An upstairs game room with half bath is perfect area for a movie night and/or playroom for children. The large primary retreat includes an ensuite bathroom with both a stand up shower and a massive soaker tub. The home has been freshened up with new backyard fencing, new carpet, and fresh paint throughout (July 2023). The home has an ideal location as its minutes away from various dining, entertainment, and shopping options. Close proximity to Klein ISD schools and Hwy 249 makes for easy drop offs and commutes. Set an appointment to make this your new home! Contact me for more information!
